    "client_msg_id": "12161806-e9a4-4c5a-8d54-715c58ed4d85",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hi y'all. Just joined after <@UDRF3ALP4> mentioned this slack to me :wave::skin-tone-2:. It seemed like the place I should be while I think hard about how to solve today's challenges of web coding &amp; design in my role as Product Manager for :fire::fox_face::hammer_and_wrench: Firefox DevTools.\n\nMy goals are to make devs more productive and guide their work to create an open, fast &amp; compatible web, accessible to everyone. I like to explore topics around logging, step debugging, logpoints/tracepoints, time travel debugging :male-scientist::skin-tone-3:, remote debugging, worker debugging, etc. (If you are interested in exploring DevTools, discussing ideas with the team or following development, we got <https://devtools-html-slack.herokuapp.com/)> .",
